&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.epid.gov.lk/web/index.php?option=com_casesanddeaths&amp;amp;Itemid=448&amp;amp;lang=en&quot;&gt;Sri Lanka Epidemiology Unit: Dengue Surveillance Trends&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.meteo.gov.lk/index.php?lang=en&quot;&gt;Sri Lanka Department of Meteorology&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
