&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.vmgd.gov.vu/vmgd/index.php/forecast-division/tropical-cyclone/track&quot;&gt;Vanuatu Meteorology and Geohazards Department: Tropical Cyclone Forecast Tracking Map&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
